# ============================================================================
# Docker and deployment configurations
.cursor/Dockerfile @devops-team @security-team
docker-compose*.yml @devops-team
scripts/ @devops-team @orchestra-ai-team

# CI/CD pipeline configurations
.github/ @devops-team @orchestra-ai-team

